metadata.name: regular bird #1
metadata.description:
regular bird no 1 - one of 600 regular birds who migrated to Ethereum together with 1 sir bird, 9 babe birds, 40 cool birds and 150 nerd birds. 

800 is the finite supply for birdjpg on Ethereum - controlled by smart contract. 

Originating on the XRPL in the year 2022, birdjpg initially minted a total supply of 8008 birdjpgs. Every birdjpg on Ethereum has a burned NFTokenId on the XRPL but uses the same jpg ipfs. Same jpg - different blockchain and different supply. 

Welcome to birdjpg. 
 - get bird.
